snippet.title: A public letter to AMBER HEARD from a survivor of DV (Letter Only)
snippet.description:
Hello All,
Thank you for the over whelming love and support that you have shown for our first upload. 
We have decided to clip just the statement so people can hear it as soon as they hit play.
THIS IS A PUBLIC LETTER TO AMBER HEARD FROM A SURVIVOR OF DV

Please follow us on twitter @JusticeForSurv4

If you would like to share a story please email us at justiceforsurvivors2021project@gmail.com

And follow the cards at the end of the video for amazing content provided by all the wonderful creators shown on screen.

#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JusticeForSurvivors #SheDoesNotSpeakForMe #SheDoesNotSpeakForUS #HoldAHAccountable
